General.Name: Onlineformapro SA
General.Description: SA Onlineformapro operates an e-learning platform for SMEs, training organizations, universities, and large groups. The company offers ONLINE AUTHOR, a suite of web tools to create assessments and online training modules; OnlineAgora to set up collaborative portals or community portals; OnlineVisio tool to vary the learning methods while keeping traces of learner activity; and Onlineformapro, a web solution to support in the production and animation of teaching methods. It also provides support and maintenance services. The company was founded in 1999 and is based in Vesoul, France.
